Registry

devdoc.details: Stores human-readable keys associated with addresses, like DNS information (see https://wiki.parity.io/Parity-name-registry.html). Needed primarily to store the address of the `TxPermission` contract (see https://wiki.parity.io/Permissioning.html#transaction-type for details).
